37476>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37476>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37477>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37478>>>    End_Procedure
37479>>>    
37479>>>End_Object
